 - Instrumental profile
 - Output AIC and BIC (N-> ndata, Nvar -> n.variables)
   r_i = (data-model) / sigma
   chi2 = sum(r_i^2)
   aic = N*log(chi2/N) + 2*Nvar
   bic = N*log(chi2/N) + ln(N) * Nvar